Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:20.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:22.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:29.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:40.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:43.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:49.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:55.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:02.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:07.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:09.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:16.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:27.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:30.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:35.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:41.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:49.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:55.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:02:00.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:02.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:15.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:20.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:22.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:29.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:35.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:39.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:43.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:02:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We swore to reunite with my crewmate\Noff some capes. His name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know that whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea one of the people\NLaboon has been waiting for...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was that skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love that bag of bones\Nand that whale, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm getting excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a musician, a talking skeleton,\Nhas an afro, goes "Yo ho ho!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was Laboon's pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming aboard our ship,\Neven if I have to drag him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's joining our crew! Any objections, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there were, would you change your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna help him see Laboon again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got my vote, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here, dummy!\NI'm not afraid of that skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a given. I'm more concerned\Nabout stopping Nami-san's marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to raid the place. Don't we\Nhave one more shadow to recover now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet! Guys, get ready for our counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna knock\NThriller Bark outta the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Food, Nami, and Shadows!!\NLuffy's Enraged Counterattack!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this pole?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might as well see what's at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. I coulda sworn\Nmy arms could stretch...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird! Did I dream that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if my legs can stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that an earthquake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! He's a stinking zombie,\Nso why does Oars have such a free spirit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is he doing up there?\NHe's making a ruckus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they don't stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, darn. I'll just have to climb.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man! Hunting down the\Nzombies with our shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sounds like it's gonna be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Luffy's zombie is a real monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's over twice the size of your average giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure you guys can beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Size isn't the only issue!\NLuffy, he has your shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z-Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Size and strength mean nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to get Luffy's shadow\Nback is to take him down, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to search for the zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I would like to see mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stay like this, we'll never get to\Nwalk under the light of the sun again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But remember what that\Ngrandpa zombie told us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw what you just did!\NYou're terribly strong, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what did you wanna discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a man I would like you to defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you could take him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has created countless victims,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all of whom could be saved if you defeated him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we take out Gecko Moria,\Neveryone will get their shadow back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, that's what he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's cutting to the heart\Nof the problem again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And isn't Moria at the top of that staircase?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! He's dead on again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, I'm gonna kick Moria's butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way everyone will get their shadow back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, you're in charge of rescuing Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better believe I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t care if he’s an invisible\Nman or a dismissible sham!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:08:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kick him to the ends of this fog!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crash that wedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I forgot to mention this earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that invisible man\Nogled at Nami in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fire him up any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid he might transform into something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, invisible man! You're gonna pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! He exploded!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad about letting Nami get\Nwhisked away right before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going with Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I don't wanna run\Ninto that Warlord again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That skeleton's duel has me concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Straw Hat throttles Moria\Nbefore he gets to fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that will be the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll have a problem on our hands\Nif his shadow trashes him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll join you, Franky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the zombie of a legendary samurai\Ncapable of? I'm dying to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-chan and the skeleton...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply put, they're the ones\Nwho need immediate help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, subduing Moria\Nis key to claiming victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, you're making this sound simple,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's one of the Seven Warlords!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a problem! So was Crocodile, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you don't see the problem?!\NHe nearly killed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you! Please be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already spelled this out loud\Nand clear, but your zombie is insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on my way, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:11:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are for you. Guys, you each get a bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They contain my special\NZombie Ascension Salt Balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is this what you were making\Nback there? I should have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have no sense of danger,\Nso let me make this perfectly clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because these waters\Nare shrouded in thick fog
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't guarantee safety from the sunlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only safe because it's night!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, consider your drop-dead\Ntime limit to be dawn, when the sun rises!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, you can't\Nforget about this time limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely right! It'd suck\Nif I couldn't eat before dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna make you rue the\Nday you picked a fight with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gecko Moria, we're taking back\Ntwice the amount of food you stole!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And before dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no. That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to recover your shadows by--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's go!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Uh, no. I meant--\N--Nami-san! Take my hand, honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This spells trouble! I need to\Nhurry and inform the master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! This is a ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neat! Too cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see squat on these waters,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I see a great future ahead of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a close one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All righty! With this ship,\NI'm gonna become King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Oars right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has climbed to the top of the mast, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Really now, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't enjoy our Laidback Fever
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with that massive, dream-filled\Nzombie wandering around the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard is rottin' bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him be! It's just a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll calm down before long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Oars on our side,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be able to steal shadows\Nfrom stronger pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start creating\NSpecial Zombies left and right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to need stronger mario, Hogback!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hogback-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Big news! The pirates are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the matter, Hildon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three pirates we just stole\Nshadows from awoke on their ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming back with their crewmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people we stole shadows from\Ncouldn't possibly be awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It looks like their friends\Nwhacked them awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to have ties with\Nthe Humming Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe he must have tipped them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As proof, all of the pirates\Nknow how to purify the zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The zombies are afraid of the pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, they are currently\Nrunning for their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is rottin' bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wild Zombies, Surprise Zombies,\Nand Soldier Zombies
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,didn't stand a chance against them\Nbefore they knew about salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send the General Zombies after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can defeat the pirates\Nwithout getting fed salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nwhere the heck is Absalom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His wedding ceremony is about to start...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The majority of the General Zombies\Nare attending his wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is wrong with those idiots?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes! Hogback-sama, he'd like\Nyou to get everyone pumped up
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the reception in an hour\Nwith your belly dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I could. Wedding ceremonies\Nare memories that last a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should make it fun and exciting--\NThis isn't the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make him cancel the wedding right this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I am merely a zombie, so I can't\Ntell Absalom-sama what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This incident doesn't call for that beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we weaken them with my ghosts,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Soldier Zombies should be\Nfully capable of capturing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't freak out just because they\Nlearned the zombies' weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will bring all of them here bound up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so go prepare mario for the rest of the crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kumacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has a point. She certainly is reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have expected as much\Nfrom the Ghost Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:17:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could learn a thing or two...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...from Kumacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-At any rate, it looks like everything\Nwill be all right, Moria-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? That's no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, now! We all know\Nyou weren't going to help...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stay here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play with Oars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I have a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Absalom is currently preoccupied,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please give me command over two zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. Pick out two\Nand take them with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I know just the two I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where is Moria?!\N--Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give my food back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the bastard that peeped on\NNami-san when she was bathing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's rottin' dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't even need salt.\NTheir hearts are burning with anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they worried about their shadows?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:41.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,200)}"Moria's Dance Hall"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain! Five pirates are headed\Nstraight for the dance hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:42.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}"Gyaa!" "Waah!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:44.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}"Racing to the Dance Hall"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two on the lower bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:50.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(1000,1)}"Moria's Dance Hall"\N"Perona's Room"\N"Wonder Garden"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:50.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(1000,1)}"Racing to the Dance Hall"\N"Headed for Perona's Room"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:47.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them are too much for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:50.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-These guys are rottin' bad! Retreat for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They're here!\N--Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It ticks me off when I think about how\Nthese weaklings managed to catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're willing to adore me for setting ya free,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let ya call me "Bro."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I completely forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.17,0:19:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it anymore! In my next life,\NI hope I'm reborn as a mosquito larva.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope my eyebrows curl up\Ntoo much and I become an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Luffy! Sanji! What's gotten into you two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne-ga-tive! Ne-ga-tive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, what just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.23,0:20:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those ghosts did it! They can\Ndishearten you with a touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As of right now, we don't\Nknow how to counter them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet! I caught him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ne-ga-tive! Ne-ga-tive!\N--Crap! They caught both of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! Now that it's come to this--!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lead Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we lose heart like them, it's game over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our only hope is to carry them and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ghosts are coming after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't want everyone to get caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks seriously bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set sail! Set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:20:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that...? No, it couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wasn't expecting that!\NThe stairs have completely vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What was that? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bunch of zombies, Usopp, and Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole lot of them fell\Nwhen the stairs gave out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about those two\Nwho came hurtling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.90,0:22:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came out of nowhere\Nand it's blocking our path!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this wall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.18,0:22:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow... What was that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.23,0:22:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't made out of stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It wasn't effective?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.58,0:22:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! What the heck are you two doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.57,0:22:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, this wall suddenly appeared in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.37,0:22:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! That's no wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is Luffy's zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.37,0:22:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.18,0:23:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.77,0:23:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.85,0:23:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...z-zombie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:27.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,700)}"On the next episode, Oars' entry into\Nthe fight suddenly changes everything!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now do you see just how\Nterrifying my ghosts are?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.94,0:23:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wipe out your entire crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.72,0:23:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I won't let you wipe us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone can talk big!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.17,0:23:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Negative Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.27,0:23:38.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nami, who has gone missing..."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.97,0:23:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've made one terrible mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:40.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"...is getting married?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.73,0:23:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Usopp's the Strongest?\NLeave Anything Negative to Him!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.62,0:23:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
